quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  22,38,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yama ikingira bamwe bayemeye bimwe vy’ukuri, ntankeka rero Imana ntikunda umuntu adashima kandi w’umuhakanyi wayo"
  22,39,Harekuriwe gusa bamwe batewe kubera yuko bahemukiwe imitima yabo mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi bwukubafasha
  22,40,"Abakuwe mungo zabo atakuri kurimwo mugabo kumpamvu yuko bavuze bati:- Umuremyi wacu niyo Mana, niyaba Imana itabakingiye abantu bamwe muribo, ntankeka abantu bari gusenyura amasengero n’ayandi masengero avugirwamwo izina ry’Imana mugihe cose, kandi ntankeka Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi n’intsinzi ihagije"
  22,41,"Abo twatsimbataje ngaha kw’Isi n’abahagarika amasengesho nugutanga imperezwa hamwe nugutegeka mukugira ibikorwa vyiza hamwe nugutuza amabi ayariyo yose aho aherereye, n’ingaruka ry’ibintu vyose niku Mana yonyene"
  22,42,Nibaguhakana umenye yuko bahakanye abamyeho imbere yabo bantu b’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Aadi (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Thamudu (iii)
  22,43,N’abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) hamwe n’abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii)
  22,44,"N’abantu bo kwa Mad’yana hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) nabone baramuhakanye nca ndabaha ikiringo cabo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri nca ndabashira muminwe yanje, mbega ibihano vyanje vyababereye gute"
  22,45,"N’ibisagara bingahe twahoneje vyamye bihemuka, hanyuma haca harwa hejuru y’ibisakazo vy’inzu zabo, n’amariba angahe y’amazi vyatawe hamwe n’amazu yari akoma komeye cane"
  22,46,"Mbega ntibagenda genda kuri iy’Isi kugira ngo baronke imitima n’ubwenge bwugutegera canke amatwi yukwumvirako, mu vy’ukuri amaso y’umuntu ntaronka ubuhumyi, mugabo imitima iri mubikiriza vy’abantu niyo ironka ubuhumyi"
  22,47,"Baraguhimiriza ngo ubazanire ibihano, mugabo Imana ntizota indagano yayo, mu vy’ukuri umusi umwe Kumuremyi wawe nink’imyaka igihumbi nkuko mwebwe muyiharura"
  22,48,"N’ibisagara bingahe nahaye isango mugihe bahemuka, munyuma ndabafata mukuboko kwanje n’iwanje niho abantu bose bazogarukira"
  22,49,"Vuga uti:- emwe bantu! ntakeka jewe kuri mwebwe ndimuba gabisha kandi mboneka neza k’umugaragaro"
  22,50,Rero abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza bazo girirwa imbabazi hamwe n’imigisha yabo y’iteka ntangere
  22,51,Nabarya bihangana muguhakana amajambo yacu abo nibo bantu bo mumuriro udahera
  22,52,"Natwe ntitwigeze turungika imbere yawe intumwa y’Imana yahawe igitabu canke intumwa y’Imana itahawe igitabu cayo bwite, mugabo mugihe yasomye Shetani ica ishiramwo inzigo muri ivyo bisomwa vyiwe, mugabo Imana ica ikuramwo ivyo Shetani yashizemwo inzigo yavyo, hanyuma Imana igaca ikomeza amajambo yayo matagatifu, nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  22,53,"Kugira ngo ikore ivyotera Shetani ingorane ziri hagati y’abantu bafise ingwara ziri mumitima yabo kandi nayo imitima yabo ikomeye cane, ntankeka mubahemukiye imitima yabo naba canamwo bimwe biri kure y’ukuri"
  22,54,"Kugira ngo bamenye abahawe ubumenyi yuko ari ivy’ukuri kuvuye Kumuremyi wawe kandi bayemere, kandi kugira ngo imitima yabo igamburuke, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ibarongora bamwe bemeye bimwe vy’ukuri munzira igororotse"
  22,55,Bazoguma babandanya bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri kuba bari mumpungenge kugeza aho umuhero w’Isi uzobashikira giturumbuka canke bashikirwe n’ibihano vy’umusi atamahoro bizoba bibafitiye
  22,56,"Ubwami bw’uwo musi buzoba ari ubw’Imana yonyene gusa ari nayo izocira urubanza ruri hagati yabo, rero bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikogwa vyiza, bazoba bari mumirima myiza ifise imigisha ntangere"
  22,57,Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri nuguhakana amajambo yacu matagatifu abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bibatetereza
  22,58,"Nabamwe bimutse kubera idini ry’Imana hanyuma bakicwa canke bagasandaba, ntankeka Imana izobahemba, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nziza isasagaza imigisha yayo kuri bose"
  22,59,Izobinjiza ahantu bazo kwishima bonyene kandi ntankeka niyo ifise ubumenyi kandi niyo ntore